introduction: AboutActress most well known for her appearances in shows like Shameless and Happyland. She is well recognized for her portrayal of Rachel in the 2015 television movie Babysitter's Black Book.Before FameShe graduated from the New World School of the Arts in 2011.TriviaShe was cast alongside Louis Mandylor and Ashley Scott in the thriller Statute of Limitations.Family LifeShe was born Angeline Fioridella Appel in Miami, Florida to Caroline Appel. In 2016, she began dating actor Noah Centineo. She'd later begin dating actor Peyton Meyer in 2018.Associated WithShe earned her first acting credit appearing alongside Cleopatra Coleman and Ryan Guzman in the 2012 film Step Up Revolution. In 2018 she began dating Peyton Meyer
